To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private Variance _var;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_var = VAR(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_var.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "variance", _var.Current.Value);
}
